{"tid":2143031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國「淨網行動」封殺中電信/阿里巴巴/騰訊","createTime":"2020-08-07T00:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T01:04:27.000Z","uid":36494,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"935cb7ac401efee866a3d75f7ca180e35e06d649","tid":2143031,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:06:53.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】中美科技戰有升級迹象。美國批評中國科技巨企旗下的TikTok、WeChat等應用程式對美國構成重大威脅，擔心阿里巴巴、百度、中國移動等中國雲端服務巨企竊取資訊，提出「淨網」（Clean Network）行動，擴大封殺中國科技龍頭，將被指為「不可靠」的中國應用程式或企業摒除在美國以外。學者指出，中國奉行「數碼威權主義」，美方發動淨網行動作反制，估計中國科網商將受嚴重衝擊，在向外擴張上嚐到碰壁滋味，走出去的野心受壓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88cbWwQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88cbWwQ.png&h=ec248972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/EJ6ZJMY52JZN5F5FWBNCA5TS7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FEJ6ZJMY52JZN5F5FWBNCA5TS7A%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=93ddd848\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FEJ6ZJMY52JZN5F5FWBNCA5TS7A%2F&h=af0fd127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/EJ6ZJMY52JZN5F5FWBNCA5TS7A/</a>"},{"pid":"349085a6eb6ce8dbc5802eccc015b3f3392cdfaf","tid":2143031,"uid":276440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7664ccf8c25b751f0384da7a8bf0122d57c0d3f5","tid":2143031,"uid":36494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:09:54.000Z","msg":"學者亦估計中國科網商將會受到嚴重衝擊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/DTZXE4OY27XHMFVLLAZYXID6HI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FDTZXE4OY27XHMFVLLAZYXID6HI%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=2570605d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FDTZXE4OY27XHMFVLLAZYXID6HI%2F&h=33f3f305\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/DTZXE4OY27XHMFVLLAZYXID6HI/</a><br />\n<br />\n「你有你安全，我有我唔信」，浸會大學新聞系高級講師呂秉權表示，美國開始發動全方位科技戰攻勢，不僅涉及軟硬件，也包括網絡基礎建設，相信對中國經濟增長造成一定衝擊。他指出，中方假設隨着中國科技的高速發展，中國經濟發展目標將會達成；中國科技增長不僅僅着眼於國內，而是輻射全世界，若中國科企外擴碰壁，科技版圖不能擴張，對中國經濟增長將造成一定影響。<br />\n<br />\n「中方先建圍牆　美反制」<br />\n<br />\n美國擴大封殺行動，有外媒形容儼如築下數碼柏林圍牆。美國約翰霍普金斯大學韋森費特政治經濟學教授孔誥烽指出，中方先建下數碼圍牆，限制美國科企進入，美方才作出反制。他指出，中國2017年實施網絡安全法，要求在華企業將個人訊息及商業數據存放在中國境內，並向安全機構提供技術支持以及通過國家安全審查等，引發巨大爭議。"},{"pid":"7c25d202a44678542ff276f6f0f9672e95b51440","tid":2143031,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:10:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5516f9a27ad79213d4ab064f291edc1a5bb58bde","tid":2143031,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:13:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f4e0e9b81c7990c0143377ddf758059746135286","tid":2143031,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:13:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f9e1486fd6696d75db2a4462fb4e9fc0e89a5258","tid":2143031,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:13:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"12067971ed66f0976ab692783075170dac7e444a","tid":2143031,"uid":22590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7c25d202a44678542ff276f6f0f9672e95b51440","tid":2143031,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:10:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:14:23.000Z","msg":"你搞我科網, 我搞你捕魚網"},{"pid":"3d018eb44f9434c3b6b669b22632a28c8010fa22","tid":2143031,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12067971ed66f0976ab692783075170dac7e444a","tid":2143031,"uid":22590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7c25d202a44678542ff276f6f0f9672e95b51440","tid":2143031,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:10:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:14:23.000Z","msg":"你搞我科網, 我搞你捕魚網"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9454decf4c9065cd80909bbf692364a3c8ca5938","tid":2143031,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:16:58.000Z","msg":"林鄭快出手反制，禁止公務員使用美帝科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6063260c31de7fdaa9aafb75f603a16b909adc64","tid":2143031,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:18:59.000Z","msg":"比拜登一上台<br />\n全面恢復中美美好關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0914e46fe697d69f6ea6324f7126470e4866f1c3","tid":2143031,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ptxSF2T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FptxSF2T.jpg&h=44893f2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edb7babe5de33af37933984c1f41eef5b5605595","tid":2143031,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:19:55.000Z","msg":"呢個真係核彈黎<br />\n中国專心內循環啦"},{"pid":"d8931d8373c57fa03e1828d4d54d0e30e80393de","tid":2143031,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:20:06.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧昨日提出針對中國網絡商及手機應用程式的擴大「潔淨網絡」計劃，雖然未有講明針對香港，但基於美方取消香港特殊地位，加上<span class=\"red\">香港電訊商、科網以至一般企業均有和內地網絡商合作，業界人士直言會對香港造成極大影響，不但打擊創科發展，甚至會波及日常生活。有初創企業表明，為免失去美國市場，決定撤出香港。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/23UJAKHO7I2CSBWLSE3NOHPSCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2F23UJAKHO7I2CSBWLSE3NOHPSCY%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=b3471727\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2F23UJAKHO7I2CSBWLSE3NOHPSCY%2F&h=1eb90c54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/23UJAKHO7I2CSBWLSE3NOHPSCY/</a>"},{"pid":"d9df3de08b6f146a7a0f6a4e52ed99c940d54ed6","tid":2143031,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9454decf4c9065cd80909bbf692364a3c8ca5938","tid":2143031,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:16:58.000Z","msg":"林鄭快出手反制，禁止公務員使用美帝科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:20:11.000Z","msg":"計數機 calculator 轉曬用算盤先<br />\n今鑊賣算盤發達了<br />\n幾時有算盤廠上市即入<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34aa58667f1344cbb579f62cdafdf7794800e8d0","tid":2143031,"uid":57309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:26:24.000Z","msg":"pompeo <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪又想犯國安法"},{"pid":"fe0d554625b3318d0ac00c9fb89202da19e08a00","tid":2143031,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:32:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"022186b5bdd88ca12910052c519c2cc5f56b63b8","tid":2143031,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T00:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef162395ed3d547de87fbbc88e2889d92660eed6","tid":2143031,"uid":300